    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a vacation or a break. i don't even know who i am if i'm not this researcher. if the work is gone, there's nothing left. it feels like i'm just a hollow shell going through the motions. it's like there's no version of my life where this doesn't hurt. i just want the noise to stop for good.",
